        <p><strong>Toronto is sometimes called "New York without the attitude" or "New York run by the Swiss."</strong> Some Torontonians love the comparison; others find it reductive. As you visit, form your own opinion ‚Äî what makes Toronto uniquely itself, beyond the NYC shadow?</p>
